**Key changes vs original:**
| Property | Before | After | Why |
|---|---|---|---|
| `.navInner` `flex-wrap` | missing (defaults to `nowrap` in theory, but no guarantee without explicit declaration) | `flex-wrap: nowrap` **explicit** | Locks the row. Without this, browsers may reflow the row under squeeze even with `flex-shrink: 0` on children. |
| `.logo` `min-width` | missing | `min-width: max-content` | Prevents the browser from assigning the flex item a box smaller than its content even when `flex-shrink: 0` is set — closes the gap in certain WebKit layout passes. |
| `.links` `overflow` | missing | `overflow: hidden` | Clips excess tagline content inside the yield container so pressure cannot reverse-propagate leftward to the logo. |
| `.tagline` `flex-shrink` | implicit | `flex-shrink: 1` explicit | Makes the yield contract explicit and auditable. |

